               Release (26.02.94).Old version: v2.5a (16.09.93).



    INTRODUCTION
    ~~~~~~~~~~~~
    VBD is a multi-purpose virus killer able to find and remove any type of
    virus.  It can also learn or analyse  new types of bootblocks.  VBD has
    a personal bank (within the main  program)  that contains more than 800
    known programs, and optionally  uses  a  learn  file  (found in the 'S'
    directory).

                               @{" Features " link features}
                               @{" Requirements " link requirements}

                               @{" Installation " link installation}
                               @{" How to use VBD " link running.vbd}
                               @{" Gadgets " link gadgets}
                               @{" Menus " link menus}

                               @{" How to Register " link register}

                               @{" About SHI " link about.shi}
