    Erik Lřvendahl Sřrensen              International"   and    a    self-
    Snaphanavej 10                       addressed  envelope  if  you  want
    4720 Prćstř                          information about SHI by letter).
    Denmark
    Phone: + 45 55 99 25 12
    Fax:   + 45 55 99 34 98
@endnode

@node about.vbd " About VBD "

    VBD v2.6 has been successfully tested on the following  Amigas:

            - A500  Kick v1.2 (Ram 512 Ko)
            - A500  Kick v1.3 (Ram 1 Meg)
            - A500+ Kick v2.0 (Ram 1 Meg)
            - A1200 Kick v3.0 (Ram 2 Meg)
            - A1200 Kick v3.0 (Ram 2 Meg)  HD 250 Meg Fast:6 MB
            - A2000 Kick v2.0 (Ram 2 Meg)  HD 40 Meg
            - A4000 Kick v3.0 (Ram 16 Meg) HD 200 Meg FPU 68882

    Author:                                               Cheveau Frédéric.
